SubjectOrder Amending the Order Declaring an Amnesty Period (2006)
PrecisOrder Amending the ORDER DECLARING AN AMNESTY PERIOD (2006) in order to extend the amnesty period protecting individuals from incurring criminal liability under the Criminal Code as a result of the illegal possession of unregistered non-restricted firearms, for one year from May 17, 2013 to May 16, 2014.
